{"tid":981315,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"334學制下嘅副學士制究竟係咪害人？","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T06:19:32.000Z","uid":208722,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f4fdc09fc84dcc7620f874b563479be5645c5cb6","tid":981315,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:14:56.000Z","msg":"Asso係當年政府為拉低失業率而整嘅學位，旨在塞多啲人繼續讀書，唔好令太多人讀完基本中學課程出嚟就失業<br />\n<br />\n但喺舊有CE AL學制下，Asso都當係畀預科失手嘅同學再多一次機會，去試下駁上去讀degree，咁講我都叫你講得通啦。因為上得預科嘅人，經歷過CE篩走班唔讀書嘅人，一般都係肯讀書嘅，想入大學嘅。咁Asso就提供個機會畀佢當多條路入大學，當然都有人係為咗逃避工作<br />\n<br />\n但而家334冇咗篩選機制，有心讀同冇心讀嘅同學都可以揀唔同副學士課程嚟讀。咁會唔會變到好多人純粹只為逃避工作就入去讀？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a842a7b9eeb845ab26cdfb0139736b6f3e0d0ad","tid":981315,"uid":140737,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"有得become another person, 老西都讀啦"},{"pid":"76113b2cdda7e7238d241fa8ce5eb6ddedd60eb1","tid":981315,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79b130d844a669d893d3dbed6fd46298f267696c","tid":981315,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a842a7b9eeb845ab26cdfb0139736b6f3e0d0ad","tid":981315,"uid":140737,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"有得become another person, 老西都讀啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T09:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1ce4762b0f91aa4c5b0e16429af1d5b5a01e7c","tid":981315,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"79b130d844a669d893d3dbed6fd46298f267696c","tid":981315,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a842a7b9eeb845ab26cdfb0139736b6f3e0d0ad","tid":981315,"uid":140737,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:16:26.000Z","ms